---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Innovation as standard" id="about">

  <Fragment slot="lead">
    At T2K Group, we are <span class="gradient-text">committed to innovation</span> and we are always looking for new ways to improve our products and services to meet the <span class="gradient-text">needs of our customers</span>.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="#testimonials"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 border-2 border-current"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="book" class="h-8" />
      <span>Testimonials</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="mailto:admin@clockr.net"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 border-2 border-current"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="envelope" class="h-8" />
      <span>Contact us</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
